HB 384 Original 2026 Regular Session Berault
Designates the portion of U.S. Hwy. 11 between Carollo Dr. and Kostmayer Ave. in St.
Tammany Parish as the "Dan DeBlanc American Hero Highway".
Directs the Dept. of Transportation and Development (DOTD) or its contractors to erect and
maintain appropriate signage reflecting this designation provided local or private monies are
received by the DOTD equal to its actual costs for material, fabrication, mounting posts, and
installation of the signage, not to exceed the sum of $2,250 per sign.
